{"tid":1684797,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警稱有權要求任何人除面罩 不服從會警告後用武力除下","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T10:34:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"974a7dd5ab653dfcd7c4d290f89f8584e24715b7","tid":1684797,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:23:27.000Z","msg":"警方表示，慶祝萬聖節容許戴面具及稍作打扮，但在禁蒙面法下警方有權在公眾地方要求任何人除下面罩、蒙面物品或抹去面上彩繪，以核實身分，如果不服從，警員會先警告、使用武力除下蒙面物品，並有權作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交平台上載的短片說，任何人都要遵從相關要求，又指出如果慶祝活動出現暴力行為，可能變成非法集結，市民不能再戴蒙面物品。<br />\n<br />\n警方預計中環大量人群聚集，中午後已封閉德己立街、和安里和蘭桂坊，黃昏後實施單向人潮管制，要由皇后大道中進入德己立街；銅鑼灣和太子可能有其他節慶活動，港鐵太子站和中環站分別在下午2時和9時關閉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A4%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%8D%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%BE%8C%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%8B-090022654.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25A4%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%2599%25A4%25E4%25B8%258B-090022654.html&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA%2BzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=45a74b7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%A6%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%AC%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A4%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%8D%E5%BE%9E%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E5%BE%8C%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%8B-090022654.html</a>"},{"pid":"4b5622887407ce7db4569edce6f9380903b6bbaf","tid":1684797,"uid":152976,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"又釋法?"},{"pid":"7a7a9f7c7661746cb03f8f8c0981287af56e22f5","tid":1684797,"